{
  "stem": "942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were many-- this patient, you know, after we operated on him, he was put back into the SS ambulance, and he was taken away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never heard from him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, at least, I don't know where they took him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had some very-- some shootings, that people were shot with a machine gun, and their bones were shattered, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I don't know, do you-- would I-- have to describe this to you, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this bone was shattered, and they had to cut it with a saw, and with plates, put together, so his leg will not be shorter, and that type of thing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sometimes, early November, when the Americans were bombing, you know, like, we had many bombing raids over Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know, there must have been 1,000 planes coming overhead, and they were trying to bomb the factories all around.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day, they knocked out the SS hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so here we are one day, all of the sudden, two SS ambulances come in with the sirens to Auschwitz, and they come to the, to our operating room.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they are bringing in-- we have to get the patients off the table.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had to clean, disinfect everything, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember several of them were in the hallways, these SS men.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were hit by shrapnel from the bombing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to operate on them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, they were-- bones were-- you know, gashes in the heads, and all kinds of shrapnel wounds, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
